@guozhangwang 
re-ran the tests and for the 10 Sec commit phase (20 million records you'll see the latency numbers are better for 10 commit phases) and the numbers seem to align a little better.  However the results on  G43/44 and J43/44 still seem strange and I think these tests should be run separately vs part of the entire test suite.  

I have some ideas on why this could happen, but since the number look good for lower commit intervals (which is what we use of EOS) I think we can merge while look into this some more.
